data.description: NO BETTER VALUE THAN THIS MOVE IN READY ST. MAARTEN . . . in the fabulous Sun City Palm Desert 55+ Community.  $50,000+++ IN UPGRADES!  NEW Kitchen Cabinets, New beautiful Tile Flooring and Carpeting, New stainless steel Appliances, new Primary Bathroom Double Vanity with Quartz countertop and  Linen/Storage Cabinet, large walk in closet. This 2 bedroom + Den or possible 3rd Bedroom, 2 Bath Home is situated on a private corner lot with a north facing low maintenance yard with citrus trees, artificial turf and covered patio area.  Make this beautiful residence your own in the nationally renowned active adult community of Sun City Palm Desert. We offer 2 golf courses, lush lakes and waterfalls, pools, fitness centers, tennis, pickle and bocce ball courts, 3 clubhouses, billiard room, ballroom, restaurants, our own post office and some of the lowest HOA dues in the desert. Come see why Money Magazine voted us 'One of the 8 greatest places to retire in America!' Hurry this beautiful home will not last!
